OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry and
OL,6,Fcloudy day but with a few showers
OL,7,Fpossible and bright or sunny intervals
OL,8,Fbreaking through the cloud. Feeling a
OL,9,Flittle cooler than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells becoming more prolonged as
OL,13,Fcloud clears. Remaining dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith long clear spells, leading to a
OL,15,Fcold night with a frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA dry morning with some long
OL,18,Fspells of sunshine. Turning cloudier
OL,19,Fthrough the afternoon as rain spreads
OL,20,Feastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
